translation[5]{c,v,t}:
  2,89,"Bathi kwakufika isiBhalo31 kubo, sivela kuAllâh, singqina eso sikubo nangona kwakumathuba angaphambili babehleli becela kuAllâh ukuba Abanike uloyiso32 phezu kwabo bangakholwayo, kodwakwathi kwakufika oko bakwaziyo basuka bala ukukholwa kuko. Ke kaloku isiqalekiso sika- Allâh masibe phezu kwabangakholwayo"
  2,90,"Akusangcole ngako oko bathengisa ngemiphefulo yabo kuko, ngokuthi bale ukukholwa koko kutyhilwe nguAllâh, bebangwa ngumona wokuba uAllâh ngoBabalo lwaKhe Ethe Wathumela uMyalezo waKhe kuye nabani na Amthandileyo kwiziCaka zaKhe. Ngokwenza oko bazibizele ingqumbo phezu kwengqumbo. Siya kuba lihlazo (elibi) isohlwayo sabo bangakholwayo"
  2,91,"Xa kusithiwa kubo, “Kholwani koko uAllâh Akutyhilileyo,” bathi bona, “Thina sikholwa koko kwatyhilwa kuthi.” Kodwa abakholwa koko kwatyhilwa emva kwako. Nangona kuyinyaniso engqina oko kukubo. Yithi kubo: “Nababulalelani ke abaProfeti baka-Allâh ukuba ngenene niyakholwa?”"
  2,92,Inene uMûsâ wafika kuni nemiqondiso ecacileyo; kodwa phezu kwako konke oko nina nanqula ithole emva kwakhe naba ngabagabadeli
  2,93,"Yabonani! Sathabatha uMnqophiso wenu, Saphakamisa intaba yaqonga phezu kwenu (Sathi): “Bambelelani nkqi koko Sininike kona niphulaphule (kuThi).” Bathi bona, “Sivile asathobela”, neentliziyo zabo zabe zizele kukunqula ithole ngenxa yokungabi nalukholo kwabo. Yithi: “Ikukungcola into eniyiyalelwa lukholo lwenu ukuba niyakholwa.”"